data.name: Jazz Coin
data.description:
Welcome To Jazz Coin 

what is jazz coin ?
The Jazz coin network introduces a completely workable solution in terms of operating a scalable and secure, decentralized cryptocurrency platform that is capable of handling loads of 100,000 transactions per second by leveraging sharding in the core creation.
The Jazz Coin team has extensive cryptocurrency experience and have created the Jazz Coin vision with the most up to date technology.
By making a change at the core in terms of how transactions are handled, with sharding integrated as the solution.
Jazz Coin will be a fast, inexpensive, secure choice for any cryptocurrency user to prefer. Project Launch Date ( march 6, 2021 ) 
This will allow blockchain’s usability to expand in a way that does not limit the size of the blockchain in the future and will not cause lagging times.
In addition to an application that will soon be launched on Play Store for Android and App Store for iPhone devices, through which you can keep your jazz coin

Why Jazz Coin?
Thanks to Decentralized Finance (DeFi), Jazz Coin offers users the ability to earn money by Staking, Pre-Sale and Airdrops on our single platform without risk of losing their funds. The security of our users' funds is a biggest priority for all our team.
We believe that our user is main active for our success. This belief naturally means the importance of providing quality decentralized financial services, security, transparency and ease of use.

DISTRIBUTION
The Jazz Initial Coin will be distributed during a pre-sale event, during which a portion of the received BNB coin will be exchanged for Jazz Coin, giving the project its first "price pump". After the end of the pre-sale, the undistributed jazz coin will be distributed among the users as a one-time subsidy. As previously explained, Jazz Coin has the ability to mine, and Jazz's cover (1,500,000,000) has been fixed forever. There is no way to issue more Jazz Coins. The undistributed jazz coin will be used to add liquidity to other DEX platforms such as PancakeSwap and 1 inch, some of which will be distributed in the form of Airdrop to early investors and media partners and some will be closed forever.
